VALUES('14cffc845bce40fea548eb50aaac6c19','windows','Drew Robbins','Director, Evangelism','<p>Drew Robbins is a Technical Evangelist with Microsoft focused on Visual Studio and the .NET Framework. He&rsquo;s spoken to audiences around the world on building applications that leverage the latest developer technologies from Microsoft. In his role at Microsoft, he helps customers understand the latest innovations in Visual Studio and the .NET Framework.</p>','https://devcampsstorage.blob.core.windows.net/media/Default/images/DRobbinsHeadshot.png')
